window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Planet Earth burns in nuclear flame.</p> <p>But The System was kind and wise enough to transfer all its little humans into a new world.</p> <p>Everyone has been granted a new name, a starting bonus, and a rousing kick up the backside.</p> <p>Some got a sword, some a crown, and me . . .</p> <p>A potato?!</p> <p>How am I supposed to take over the world with this thing?</p> <p>System, are you sure you're so kind and wise after all?</p>"; 
